weka.classifiers.functions.gmlvq.model

Class OmegaMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.core.matrix.Matrix
      • weka.classifiers.functions.gmlvq.model.OmegaMatrix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, RevisionHandler

    public class OmegaMatrix
extends Matrix
    The matrix describing the mapping rule which is used to project DataPoints and Prototypes to their respective EmbeddedSpaceVector.
    This matrix is of dimension dataDimension x omegaDimension. It is updated over the course of learning and can indirectly be visualized via the lambda matrix, by evaluating the expression lambda = omega * omega'.

    S
